Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and serene scene depicting Jesus walking on water during a stormy night. Show gentle moonlight casting a soft glow on the turbulent waves, with Jesus calmly and gracefully moving across the water, exuding a sense of peace and divine presence. Include subtle details like sparkling water droplets, a starlit sky, and a faint outline of a boat in the background to convey the miraculous nature of this biblical event. Capture the spiritual essence of faith, courage, and trust in the image.
